@startuml CU04_Sequence_Retrieve
!include ../_shared/global_style.iuml
skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
autonumber "<b>"

title CU-04 — Gestionar recursos de lección: Retrieve con S3 URL

actor Estudiante as Actor
boundary "Angular\nLessonComponent" as Angular
control "ResourceViewSet\n(resource_viewset.py:62)" as ViewSet
entity "ResourceSerializer\n(resource_serializer.py)" as Serializer
entity "Resource\n(resource_model.py:8)" as Model
database "NeonDB\nPostgreSQL" as DB

Actor -> Angular : Ver recurso de lección
Angular -> ViewSet : GET /api/v1/resources/{id}/\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>

ViewSet -> ViewSet : get_permissions() → [IsAuthenticated()]
ViewSet -> Model : get_object()
Model -> DB : SELECT * FROM resource\nWHERE pk = {id} AND is_deleted = False
DB --> Model : Resource instance

ViewSet -> Serializer : ResourceSerializer(instance)
note right
    file field serialized as
    S3 URL (public-read or
    pre-signed depending on config)
end note
Serializer --> ViewSet : { id, lesson, file: "<S3 URL>",\nresource_type, title, created_at }
ViewSet --> Angular : HTTP 200
Angular --> Actor : Renderizar recurso / enlace de descarga

@enduml
